Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:10.72,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:12.02,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.19,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.27,0:00:19.57,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol som...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.85,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... celú dobu tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:25.70,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Celú dobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:28.33,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Pred chvíľou si omdlel a zrútil sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:37.62,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To znamená, že neubehol žiaden čas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:38.57,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:39.87,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,A čo tieňová Yuuko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:41.26,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tieňová Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:43.63,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tá ktorá nás predtým naháňala.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:49.88,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi znovu donútila Yuuku-san na to zabudnúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:55.37,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Odstránila ju zo svojho vedomia a zničila jej existenciu zo svojej mysle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:56.96,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:00:58.44,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... môžeš vstať?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:00.29,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:07.28,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa stalo, Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:09.97,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun, ty si...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:11.82,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Moja minulosť...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:14.40,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:16.76,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje spomienky na minulosť...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:17.90,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:20.50,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san! Yuuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:30.88,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:31.92,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... kde si?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:33.94,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun, kde si?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:35.88,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje, Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:38.11,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun, kde sa nachádzaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:40.34,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu som! Ja som tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:41.24,TOA011t,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpovedz mi, Teiichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.30,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san, čo sa to deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:42.22,TOA011t,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpovedz mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.08,TOA011t,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:45.10,TOA011t,,0000,0000,0000,,Neopúšťaj ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:47.62,TOA011t,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:47.62,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san...
