Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:36.93,TOA11h,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.05,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.46,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Asi znovu nepríde.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:19.03,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Som si istá, že tu bude...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.32,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Určite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:31.55,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Keďže si sa dozvedel o Yuukinej minulosti, \Ntak sa muselo stať toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:36.21,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuukine spomienky sa odstránili tesne pred jej smrťou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.21,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolo to veľmi smutné.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.94,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Priveľa utrpenia na jedinú osobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:47.20,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že tieto spomienky vytvorili kópiu spomienok v tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:48.44,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale to je...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:53.18,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,A preto Yuuko, uzavrela svoje vedomie aj pred tebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:57.11,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To znamená, že si sa stal presne takým, ako aj tieňová Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.44,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To snáď nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:01.10,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko nedokáže vidieť tieňovú Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:04.63,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Niekedy, jej spúšťač spôsobí, že ju na okamih môže vidieť...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.93,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... lenže ihneď to potlačí a už ju nedokáže vidieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.01,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám z toho obavy o teba, Niiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:19.47,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Dnes nebudeš jesť?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:22.59,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, nemám vôbec chuť na jedlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.91,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooch? Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:27.91,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.36,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:30.11,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:31.90,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Óch, vôbec nič!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:34.82,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.09,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... si to ty, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:41.50,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje, Niiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:49.08,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tušila som to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:54.89,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to také, ako keby sa Teiichi-kun stal duchom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.02,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Som duch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.91,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikto si neuvedomuje moju existenciu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:21.93,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:23.35,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.48,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie je pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.42,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikto ma nevidí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:29.01,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja ťa vidím.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.56,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikto nepočuje môj hlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:33.38,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja ho počujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.81,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikto sa ma nedotýka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:46.42,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,NIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.74,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to také, ako keby som sa stal duchom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:02.99,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:08.22,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to bude takto pokračovať, jedného dňa na mňa Yuuko-san zabudne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:12.07,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ľudia a duchovia, by sa aj tak nemali zaplietať.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.92,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno to bolo iba dočasné, kým to skončí.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.81,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je? Žiadna reakcia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.87,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravdepodobne máš pravdu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:27.54,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak moje dotyky spôsobujú Yuuke-san utrpenie, \Nnemal by som sa k nej približovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:31.99,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak moja prítomnosť, ju núti pripomínať si trpkú minulosť, ktorá jej spôsobuje smútok...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:34.71,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš to naozaj vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.61,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To, že sa s ňou rozchádzaš pre jej dobro, je lož!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.22,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravdou je, že sa len priveľmi bojíš!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:41.82,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:44.51,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne si myslíš, že Yuuko toto chce?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.52,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš čo ma štve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:51.65,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Sledovať vás dvoch, ako sa po sebe zliepate, pretože si myslíte, že vás nikto iný nemôže vidieť!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:52.55,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirie-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.14,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Lenže vieš čo je ešte horšie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:57.15,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Že ani jeden z vás s tým nič nerobí!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.83,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,T-To je smiešne...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:07:59.92,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, smiešne...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.75,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozhodni sa už čo chceš! Rozhodni!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:03.97,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Miluješ Yuuko, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.33,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechceš ju stratiť, všakže?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.73,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepremýšľaj ako slobodný mládenec, aby si klamal samého seba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.64,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,T-To som nechcel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.06,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Obaja prevezmite zodpovednosť...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:16.47,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak ste sa snažili spolupracovať na všetkých tých prípadoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.18,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirie-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:23.21,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedovolím vám, aby ste sa rozišli kvôli niečomu tak malichernému!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.87,parkl,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(374,233)}Prekľajem ťa, \Nak to otvoríš!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.48,zapis,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(280,343,193,91,0,4391)}Teiichi-kun, \Nnesnaž sa\N tak veľmi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.48,zapis,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(310,384,248,224,0,3011)}Yuuko {\fnArial}|{\fnAshcan BB} Teiichi-kun 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.48,zapis,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(357,479,296,323,0,3011)}Chýbaš mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:46.74,zapis2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,359)}Chýbaš mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.22,TOA11h,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zápisník Paranormálneho Vyšetrovacieho Klubu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.17,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:57.87,zapis3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(453,316)}Aj ty mi chýbaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:01.84,zapis4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1200)\pos(321,255)}Aj ty mi chýbaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:03.95,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.56,zapis3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,0)\fs44\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(274,76)}Som osamelá.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:14.92,zapis3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,520)\fs44\pos(445,288)\3c&HFFFFFF&}Aj ja som osamelý.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:16.56,zapis3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,520)\fs44\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(201,67)}Chcem ťa vidieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:18.13,zapis3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,520)\fs44\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(464,408)}Chcem vidieť\N tvoj úsmev.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.80,zapis3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,520)\fs44\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(203,77)}Chcem počuť tvoj hlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:21.43,zapis3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,520)\fs44\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(449,447)}Chcem sa s tebou \Nrozprávať.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:23.00,zapis3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,520)\fs40\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(275,104)}Chcem, \Naby si sa ma dotýkal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:23.07,zapis3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,520)\fs44\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(453,297)}Chcem sa ťa dotknúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.10,zapis3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(275,107)}Chcem sa ťa dotknúť
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:36.45,zapis3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(275,107)}Chcem sa ťa dotknúť
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.45,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to tak hrejivé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.05,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.99,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:49.84,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.69,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj mňa to baví.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:54.29,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď ma nevidíš...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.00,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... ja ťa vidím.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.62,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Počujem tvoj hlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.22,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokonca, si môžeme takto vymieňať pocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.43,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.43,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Som tak osamelá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:06.81,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Veľmi to bolí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:09.17,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslela som, že som na to zabudla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.81,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslela som si, že som sa zbavila týchto emócií, a aj tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:13.26,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.41,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Pomôžte mi niekto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:27.95,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobré ráno prajem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.23,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dobré ráno, Okonogi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:31.87,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:33.70,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nič, vôbec nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:37.41,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Niiya-san, dnes som ti priniesla darček.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:38.68,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Na!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:40.82,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:45.42,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To sú z Okonogiho cukrárne, najznámejšie cukríky, obradné Okonogiho cukríky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.55,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Okonogiho cukráreň?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:55.33,nau,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(326,156)}Náuka
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.78,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to domáca výroba.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:55.51,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Onedlho budú znovu vypustené niektoré známe obľúbené a toto je prvý výrobok!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.50,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Má pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.60,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj chutia ako tie predtým.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:02.39,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:04.73,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Niiya-san, už si ich niekedy ochutnal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.37,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Veď tieto cukríky sa nevyrábali celé desaťročia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:09.39,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Och, nie, len sa mi to zdalo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.56,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne to má starú známu chuť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:15.60,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san, jedla tieto aj s Asou-chan, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:16.85,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Asa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:18.55,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Asa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:21.71,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,No jasné...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:22.89,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.60,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem ti, Okonogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:29.89,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nechápem o čo ide, ale som poctená, ak som mohla pomôcť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.17,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč, že ťa o to žiadam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.27,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevadí.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.50,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Veď o nič také nejde.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.15,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:38.36,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:41.86,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Moja starká, je riaditeľkou na tejto škole.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.34,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.24,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Žiadam ťa, nikomu to nehovor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:48.83,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Študenti a ani učitelia by nevedeli, ako sa majú začať ku mne správať.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.85,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto je to pre všetkých tajomstvom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.07,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:57.85,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodnes, som nepovedala svojej babičke, že môžem vidieť Yuuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.35,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:03.23,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože, by bola z toho veľmi smutná.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:06.82,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Vstúpte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.83,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňte ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:14.57,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto je moja starká, Kanoe Yukariko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:17.34,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže toto je Yuukina-san mladšia sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.34,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Dosť si už dospel, Teiichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:24.08,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirie mi rozpovedala príbeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.07,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to pravda?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.62,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokážeš aj ty vidieť Yuuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.12,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj, vravíte?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:31.63,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To znamená...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:32.96,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:36.80,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Vždy som dokázala vidieť ducha svojej staršej sestry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:42.21,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokázala som vidieť ten odporný vzhľad, poškvrnený hnevom a nenávisťou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:49.12,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tí, ktorí pochovali moju staršiu sestru, asi tiež videli tento vzhľad a to ich vydesilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:55.40,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom, veľmi dlhú dobu, bola akákoľvek diskusia o nej v dedine zakázaná.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:57.48,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:03.03,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď dospelí pomreli, tak som ako mladá dostala za úlohu viesť túto školu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:06.27,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by som vedela, že telo mojej staršej sestry je pochované niekde v starej školskej budove...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:09.16,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... nikdy by som ju nedala zbúrať a zachovala by som ju, ako pamätník.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:10.75,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.44,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... duch mojej staršej sestry neodpočíva...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.01,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... a aj naďalej navštevuje školské priestory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.44,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo iného môžem pre ňu urobiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.02,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie je pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.20,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san sa má dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.57,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Je láskavá a prekrásna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:30.30,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... ľahko sa rozhnevá, ale je vždy veselá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.91,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty ju naozaj takúto vidíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.59,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:40.74,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Je taká istá, ako keď ošetrovala Asu-chan, láskavá prekrásna staršia sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.57,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Odkiaľ o tom vieš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:45.48,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:49.41,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem sa ešte raz rozprávať s touto Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:55.20,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukariko-san, dôvodom prečo som sa s vami chcel stretnúť je to, že sa chcem viacej dozvedieť o Ase-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:56.96,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,O tom dievčati?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:05.91,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem, jej pocity sa istotne preniesli do teba, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:06.50,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.08,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri sa na to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:15.84,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Asa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.56,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte si si to nevšimol, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.80,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Táto fotka je...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.57,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:51.58,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:58.99,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:00.78,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Sneží?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:05.72,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.21,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:09.86,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to má byť?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:11.77,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:14.72,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:19.02,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie... Nie... Nie... Nie... Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.66,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie... Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:24.03,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.48,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.55,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidíš ma, Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.19,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:36.24,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Napadlo ma, že ak to urobím, tak si ma všimneš.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:41.00,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tieto predmety ktoré tu sú, sú tvoje najvzácnejšie spomienky, Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.23,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:50.83,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom ma napadlo, že ak si uvedomuješ svoju existenciu, tak dokážeš vidieť aj druhú Yuuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.12,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to tak, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:57.57,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýliš sa, Teiichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:16:00.78,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto nie som ja! To nie som ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:01.97,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.24,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:06.01,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Najvzácnejšie spomienky, ktoré si zabudla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:09.08,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Najvzácnejšie pocity, ktoré si neprijala.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:10.93,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň, prosím ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:14.46,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíš si na mňa spomenúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.16,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretrpme ten deň spoločne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.16,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.48,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj s tebou som sa chcel stretnúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.45,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď som sa ťa dotkol, videl som tvoje spomienky z minulosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:28.57,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom som zistil, čo sa stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.80,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,O ničom nevieš.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:33.26,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepoznáš skutočnú pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.19,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To nebolo všetko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.48,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Týmto to neskončilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:44.39,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemysli si, že vieš čo sa stalo len preto, že si to videl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.15,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:49.79,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nič nevieš o mojom utrpení.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:53.47,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevieš o mojom smútku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:57.42,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,O mojom výraze v tvári, keď som sa triasla strachom pred vrahmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.09,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,O vydesenom pohľade mladšej sestry, keď na mňa hľadela...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:02.98,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,O ľuďoch, ktorí vreli všetkými negatívnymi emóciami...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:06.36,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... a moje vlastné ja, ktoré ma prinútilo prevziať na seba všetko utrpenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:12.12,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetku tú nenávisť, tú bolesť, ten smútok, \Nto utrpenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:17.26,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Neurobila som nič zlého, napriek tomu som musela toto pretrpieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.73,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola som donútená znášať všetky tieto hrozné pocity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:28.22,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže ako môžeš tvrdiť, že mi rozumieš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.89,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomuto ja nerozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.37,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nerozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.75,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Lenže, aj tak ja to bolestivé!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.36,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Veď je to predsa tak smutné...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.01,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak veľmi to bolí.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.38,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedá sa nič iné, iba nenávidieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:50.61,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedá sa nič iné, len preklínať!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:55.26,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak neustále nedokážeš cítiť nič iné, len celý čas tieto emócie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:56.88,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to príliš bolestné.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:01.88,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je možné nič iné, len nenávidieť...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:05.02,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,V takejto situácii nie je možné iné, len nenávidieť!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:10.12,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď si mi ukázala tieto spomienky,\N tak ma to tiež bolelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:12.26,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol som veľmi vydesený.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.46,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,A, bolo to hrozné...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:20.19,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Kým si ty trpela, \Nja som nedokázal vôbec nič...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.31,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Len som mohol bezmocne sledovať, a nič iné...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:27.10,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto som najviac zo všetkého nenávidel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.52,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak nepredstaviteľné...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:33.95,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:36.35,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sa ma dotýkaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.75,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohto množstva nenávisti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:40.74,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohto odporného vzhľadu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:44.71,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože, aj ty si Yuuko-san, nie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:52.84,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj ty si moja Yuuko-san, ktorú tak veľmi milujem, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.72,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto... Preto...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:58.99,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.71,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň plakať.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:04.83,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.74,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:08.68,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun, ak plačeš pre mňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.93,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak plačeš pre mňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.13,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak ma takto pevne držíš...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.48,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď som tak veľmi trpela...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.47,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď som sa toho chcela zbaviť...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.76,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko sa stráca.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:23.80,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Dlho som žila iba s týmito emóciami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.63,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak dlho som ich neprijímala.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:30.74,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Lenže toto, už nie je vôbec podstatné.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.04,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:35.20,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun, je to naozaj v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:37.88,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Budem v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:40.63,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:44.57,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Veď predsa obe, ste mojou najmilovanejšou Yuukou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.40,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre mňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:49.94,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre mňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.93,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... to bude desivé.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.90,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To je už v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.09,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak ma Teiichi-kun prijal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.11,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... neexistuje žiadna ľútosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:05.07,ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(327,44)}Vitaj naspäť
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.69,ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(327,44)}moje ja
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:06.46,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Vitaj naspäť, moje ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.25,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:22.94,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Som späť, Teiichi-kun.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.12,0:20:39.82,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Osamelosť pochádzajúca zo samoty
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.51,0:20:44.19,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Dávno vyblednutý úsmev
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.98,0:20:48.56,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Čo si ukrýval si mi dal
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.36,0:20:52.52,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}všetko je mi drahé
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.86,0:20:58.05,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}I keď stojíš pri mne
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.05,0:21:02.07,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Nedotýkaš sa ma
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.53,0:21:06.53,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Moje srdce, je ako mesiac
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.53,0:21:11.16,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Neustále sa mení
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.16,0:21:15.05,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Aj nesplnené sľuby
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.68,0:21:19.37,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Aj neusušené slzy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.07,0:21:23.68,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Nechám si všetko čo si mi dal
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.48,0:21:30.31,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}V objatí tanca
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:39.89,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}hitorikiri no sabishisa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:44.37,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}hitotoki no hohoemi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:48.64,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}anata ga kureru mono wa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:52.60,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}minna itoshii
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:58.13,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}sugu soko ni ite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:02.15,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}furerarenai mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:06.61,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}kokoro wa tsuki no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:11.24,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}katachi wo kaeteku no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:15.13,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}kanawanai yakusoku mo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:19.45,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}kawakanai namida mo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:23.76,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}anata ga kureta mono wa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:30.39,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}dakishimete odoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:22:01.79,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Vtedy, zrejme všetky mená tých, ktorí tajne zosnovali ľudskú obeť, boli vytesané na pamätnej prekliatej skale.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:03.37,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:07.13,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Napokon, príčinou bola epidémia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.44,0:22:09.21,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To je už jedno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:18.54,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Opustím svoje smutné spomienky a aj šťastné spomienky, teraz ich tu všetky zanechám.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:20.71,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Och, jasné.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:22.05,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som ti ukázať toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.62,0:22:24.68,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,To je Asa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:27.08,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukariko-san mi to požičala zo svojho albumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:30.39,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Asa-chan, sa v skutočnosti volala Asagi, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.69,0:22:32.60,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Charakteristickou farbou pre "asagi"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:33.90,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... je svetlo modrá...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:37.23,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... je ju možné vidieť medzi prechodom červenej a fialovej, po súmraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:41.59,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi je vlastne, meno mojej babičky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:42.43,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.55,0:22:44.49,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak to znamená... Nemožné...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:45.35,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:47.72,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že som vnukom Asi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:54.72,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:57.06,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebolo to zbytočné.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:22:57.51,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:23:01.29,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Netrpela som len tak zbytočne...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:03.54,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Asa-chan dokázala prežiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:06.76,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,... a ja som sa dokázala takto s tebou stretnúť, Teiichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:11.70,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun, nevadí mi byť ľudskou obeťou, ak to znamená, že môžem byť takto s tebou spojená!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:13.52,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Spojená?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:15.08,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:32.02,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Deje sa niečo, Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.15,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Vôbec nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:37.81,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Zlomené srdce je zcelené.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:40.15,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Stratený čas sa navrátil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.05,0:23:42.84,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcete to prežiť ešte raz...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.04,0:23:44.73,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Vo svojej skutočnej podobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:49.95,zav,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(658,1)\pos(464,120)}Dvanásta Záhada
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:49.95,zav,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(658,1)\pos(444,300)}Dievčina Súmraku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:47.03,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Dvanásta záhada.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.64,0:23:49.06,TOA11,,0000,0000,0000,,Dievčina Súmraku.
